FBIS3-10641 "drlat047_a_94001" FBIS-LAT-94-047 Document Type:Daily Report 10 March 1994 CARIBBEAN Cuba Fidel Castro Meets With U.S. Magazine Director FL0903154294 Havana Radio Reloj Network in Spanish 1510 GMT 9 Mar 94 FL0903154294 Havana Radio Reloj Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] The director of a U.S. magazine has visited Cuba. Mortimer Zuckerman, executive director of the magazine U.S. NEWS AND WORLD REPORT, called his first visit to Cuba fascinating because it allowed him to learn firsthand about health, the pharmaceutical industry, and biotechnology. During his stay on the island, Zuckerman met with Commander in Chief Fidel Castro, and called the meeting unforgettable and fruitful.
